  "texts": [
    "17 The construction is a possibility frame version of the construction in Litak 2005a of a CV-BAO that generates a variety of BAOs with no atomic members.",
    "(We will precisely relate full possibility frames and CV-BAOs in § § 5.1-5.3.)",
    "The main idea of the following is exactly as in Litak 2005a (also cf.",
    "Venema 2003), but where Litak defines operators on an algebra, we define relations on a frame.",
    "One may compare the two constructions to see the relative benefits of thinking in terms of relations vs. operators.Consider O -= {(a, b) | ∃⟨a ′, b ′ ⟩ ∈ σ O: ⟨a, b + |a -b| 2 ⟩ = ⟨a ′, b ′ ⟩}."
